The standard free energy is then

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \Delta G^{\circ}=-n F E_{\mathrm{cell}}^{\circ} \\
& \Delta G^{\circ}=-2 \times 96,485 \frac{\mathrm{C}}{\mathrm{~mol}} \times 1.247 \frac{\mathrm{~J}}{\mathrm{C}}=-240.6 \frac{\mathrm{~kJ}}{\mathrm{~mol}}
